This software and associated files (the "Software") implement the NiDa
wildfire early-warning research prototype. The Software is made available
for research, academic, and educational purposes under the terms below.

Author and citation details are intentionally withheld during peer review
and will be added upon publication of the associated research paper.


PERMISSIONS
-----------
You are permitted, free of charge, to:

  1. View, download, and study the source code.
  2. Run the Software locally for research, evaluation, and learning.
  3. Modify the Software for your own non-commercial research and
     educational use.


CONDITIONS
----------
  1. Attribution. Any use of the Software in academic work, publications,
     or presentations must cite the associated research paper (reference
